        <section id="product-short-information">
            <div id="product-short-text" itemprop="description">
                
    If you're working with the complex programming of SAP Business Workflow, this is the resource for you! This book addresses all aspects of the tools that are directly related to the developer’s tasks, explaining when it is necessary to influence the behavior of SAP Business Workflow using custom code, detailing how to write this code, and offering complete listings for download. 

            </div>

            <div id="product-usps">
                
    <ul class="usp">
    
    
        <li style="color: #21B7C5;"><div>Practical exercises for programming in SAP Business Workflow</div></li>
    
        <li style="color: #21B7C5;"><div>Step-by-step instructions for adapting data flows, agent determination, event definitions, and more</div></li>
    
        <li style="color: #21B7C5;"><div>Examples, problem solutions, and tips and tricks for daily practice</div></li>
    
</ul>


            </div>

